[31m-- `DEBUG_MODE`: Set to `True` to enable debug logging (default: `False`)[m
[31m-- `PERFORMANCE_MODE`: Set to `HIGH`, `MEDIUM`, or `LOW` (default: `MEDIUM`)[m
[31m-- `SHARD_COUNT`: Number of shards to use (default: `1`)[m
[31m-- `CLUSTER_ID`: Cluster ID for multi-process setups (default: `0`)[m
